---
---
<section
  class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-4 overflow-hidden"
  aria-label="메인 히어로"
>
  <!-- Background: soft gradient mesh -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-pk-bg via-pk-bg-alt to-pk-bg"></div>
    <!-- Subtle gradient orbs -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full opacity-[0.04]" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, #f0c040, transparent 70%);"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/3 right-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full opacity-[0.03]" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, #6366f1, transparent 70%);"></div>
    <!-- Top vignette -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,transparent_50%,#0a0a14_100%)]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Subtitle -->
    <p class="text-pk-text-secondary text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-6 animate-fade-up">
      POCKET KINGDOM
    </p>

    <!-- Title -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-pk-text font-bold animate-fade-up-delay-1 mb-6" style="
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    ">
      포켓 <span class="text-pk-accent">왕국</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Prophecy quote -->
    <blockquote class="glass-card-glow max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10 animate-fade-up-delay-2 text-left">
      <p class="text-pk-accent/80 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed italic">
        "어둠이 세상을 삼킨 뒤,<br/>
        잊혀진 마석의 빛이 다시 깨어나리라.<br/>
        그 빛을 이끄는 자가 세계를 되찾으리."
      </p>
      <footer class="text-pk-muted text-xs mt-3 not-italic">— 고대의 예언서</footer>
    </blockquote>

    <!-- Tagline -->
    <p class="text-pk-text-secondary text-sm md:text-base mb-10 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-fade-up-delay-3 text-balance">
      102종의 크리처와 계약하고, 18가지 타입의 상성을 읽어
      마왕에게 빼앗긴 세계를 되찾아라.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA buttons -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center animate-fade-up-delay-4">
      <a href="/" class="pixel-btn">
        지금 플레이
      </a>
      <a href="/creatures" class="pixel-btn-ghost">
        크리처 도감
      </a>
      <a href="/story" class="pixel-btn-ghost">
        스토리 읽기
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll hint -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-pk-muted/40 text-xs animate-float" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="block mb-2 text-center text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em]">SCROLL</span>
    <svg width="16" height="10" viewBox="0 0 16 10" fill="none" class="mx-auto">
      <path d="M1 1L8 8L15 1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
